title: Sports OT Rewind: 2002 Class 2A State Semifinals - Breathitt County vs. Russell
text:
/ Headlines List / Article 
JACKSON, Ky. (WYMT) - With three state championships in its history, Breathitt County has certainly played its fair share of classics, but aside from the three state championship games maybe no one game is more memorable than the one played on the night of November 29th, 2002. 
In this week's Sports Overtime Rewind, we go back to the 2002 state semifinals between the Breathitt County Bobcats and the Russell Red Devils.
